he sun\u2019s rays with its whole body."}, {"version": "black-2", "text": "If it senses strong sunlight, it opens its folded petals to absorb the sun\u2019s rays with its whole body."}, {"version": "diamond", "text": "It blooms during times of strong sunlight. It tries to make up for everything it endured as a bud."}, {"version": "heartgold", "text": "During times of strong sunlight, its bud blooms, its petals open fully, and it becomes very active."}, {"version": "legends-arceus", "text": "Motionless, save for the occasional quiver. A rich array of Pok\u00e9mon can be found gathered around it, drawn by the scent exuded from Cherrim's folded petals."}, {"version": "omega-ruby", "text": "During times of strong sunlight, its bud blooms, its petals open fully, and it becomes very active."}, {"version": "pearl", "text": "It is docile as a bud, but turns cheerful when it blooms. It folds back into a bud if sunlight wanes."}, {"version": "platinum", "text": "If it senses strong sunlight, it opens its folded petals to absorb the sun\u2019s rays with its whole body."}, {"version": "shield", "text": "Its folded petals are pretty tough. Bird Pok\u00e9mon can peck at them all they want, and Cherrim won\u2019t be bothered at all."}, {"version": "soulsilver", "text": "During times of strong sunlight, its bud blooms, its petals open fully, and it becomes very active."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "As a bud, it barely moves. It sits still, placidly waiting for sunlight to appear."}, {"version": "white", "text": "If it senses strong sunlight, it opens its folded petals to absorb the sun\u2019s rays with its whole body."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "If it senses strong sunlight, it opens its folded petals to absorb the sun\u2019s rays with its whole body."}, {"version": "x", "text": "During times of strong sunlight, its bud blooms, its petals open fully, and it becomes very active."}, {"version": "y", "text": "If it senses strong sunlight, it opens its folded petals to absorb